('P001', 'BACKSTAGE Face & Body Foundation', 'DIOR', 'Makeup', 'Face', 119.99, 'What it is:\r\nA foundation for the face and body in 40 shades with a natural, matte finish and medium, buildable coverage that\'s waterproof and sweat-resistant.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nDior Backstage Face and Body Foundation is the Dior makeup artistsí secret weapon to create a flawless, runway-ready complexion for both the face and body. This waterproof formula fuses with skin, resisting extreme conditions like workout sessions, water, and even high temperatures and humid environments. It can also be used to camouflage minor imperfections on the neck, shoulders, legs, or anywhere else. Best of all, it ís available in 40 shades with a natural, matte finish.'),
('P002', 'Natural Radiant Longwear Foundation', 'NARS', 'Makeup', 'Face', 199.99, 'What it is:\r\nA foundation with medium buildable coverage, up to 16 hours of lightweight, natural, fade-resistant wear, featuring full-powered radiance to smooth the look of skin.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nNARSí first 16-hour foundation has a lightweight, breathable, fade-resistant formula and features medium-to-full, buildable coverage in 33 skin-matching shades to fit all skin tones and undertones. The transfer-resistant, sweat-resistant formula stays color-true all day, and continues to look fresh and vibrant, as if it was just applied. This formula features superior blendability for an imperceptible effect that looks natural, like skin. It doesnít look or feel cakey, heavy, drying, or masking. A unique combination of translucent base with micronized amino acid-coated pigments and mineral tone-balancing powders mimic skinís tone, fusing with it for the closest match. NARSí Skin Optimizing Complexóa blend of raspberry, apple, and watermelon extractsóhelps support skinís elastic fibers to smooth and improve skinís appearance over time for optimal radiance.'),
('P003', 'Teint Idole Ultra Long Wear Foundat', 'LANC‘ME', 'Makeup', 'Face', 169.99, 'What it is: \r\nAn oil-free, long-wearing, liquid foundation that delivers medium-to-full coverage and leaves a natural-looking, velvety-matte finish for up to 24 hours. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nFor those long days, this foundation gives you the full coverage, comfortable, long wear that you need. Not thick or greasy, this foundation\'s innovative formula gives all skin tones flawless, complexion-perfecting coverage, while the broad spectrum SPF 15 sunscreen protects. Redness, pores, and imperfections visibly disappear, evening the skin tone and leaving a mattified-yet-natural result. Formulated with color-true NAI pigments, it maintains your skinís pH level so that color stays put all day longómeaning your makeup doesnít need to be re-touched and provides transfer-resistant coverageóplus, itís infused with perlite and silica, absorbing oil for a shine-free wear.'),
('P004', 'Shameless Youthful-Look 24H Foundat', 'MARC JACOBS BEAUTY', 'Makeup', 'Face', 199.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn innovative, medium, buildable foundation with 24-hour wear and first-to-market, flashback-free SPF 25 for a youthful look.\r\n\r\nWhat does:\r\nHave it all with Shameless Youthful-Look 24H Foundation. Inspired by Marcís very own shameless attitudeóand his tattooóthis innovative foundation lets your best self show all day long. Itís clinically tested for 24-hours of long-wear, and contains a first-to-market technology that encapsulates the SPF in pigment. This innovation makes the SPF visibly undetectable, so thereís no flashback in photos and no ashy, grey undertones in the formula. \r\n\r\nThis oil-free, weightless foundation provides buildable, medium coverage that blends seamlessly. The patented Infinity Millingô process produces super-fine pigments that result in the most natural-looking, self-setting finish. The broad shade range was developed with artists and models worldwide to fit all skin tones and skin types. The perfect level of coverage allows for flexibility across the shade rangeógo deeper or lighter depending on your desired look. \r\n\r\nShameless liquid foundation also beautifies from the inside out with skincare benefits, including phenomenal hydration. It contains snow mushroom, which is known for its impressive ability to hold onto wateróitís like natureís dupe for hyaluronic acid. The formula also contains blue daisy extract, known to visibly diminish the complexion-dulling effects of pollution. Together, they help your skin look hydrated, plumped, and more youthful. Go ahead, show off your skin shamelessly.'),
('P005', 'Ultra HD Perfector Skin Tint Foundation SPF 25', 'MAKE UP FOR EVER', 'Makeup', 'Face', 139.99, 'What it is:\r\nA revolutionary skin tint that blurs and enhances the look of skin for a perfected complexion. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThis innovative, weightless formula creates a blurring effect that enhances and perfects the look of skin. Whether youíre new to foundation or an enthusiast seeking a fresh alternative, this sheer-to-medium coverage tint flatters every face. Featuring warming pigments for a subtle, sunkissed glow and protective SP5 25, this formula keeps skin feeling supple and protected. Ultra HD Perfector breaks all of the limits weíve come to expect from foundations with a texture thatís effortless to apply with your fingertips, a nurturing formula, and a long-lasting natural finish. This is your most natural, perfected skin, on demand. \r\n\r\nUltra HD Perfector is available in 10 shades, with each individual shade spanning uniquely across multiple skin tones.\r\n'),
('P006', 'Radiant Creamy Concealer', 'NARS', 'Makeup', 'Face', 24.99, 'What it is: \r\nAn award-winning concealer that provides medium-to-full, buildable coverage and corrects, contours, highlights, and perfects. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nIdeal for all skin types, Radiant Creamy Concealer is a multi-action formula that instantly masks imperfections, blurs the look of lines and wrinkles, and hides dark circles and signs of fatigue. The botanical blend hydrates, firms, reduces redness, and strengthens the look of skin by helping its barrier retain moisture. Light-diffusing technology evens out the complexion so that skin appears fresh and natural with a radiant finish. It also delivers antioxidant protection to help shield skin against damaging free radicals. \r\n\r\nThe Mineral Tone Balancing Powder works to optically correct, not mask, imperfections. Unique powders even the skintone and provide invisible skin correction so skin that skin appears radiant, fresh, and natural. Itís infused with a Multi-Active Botanical Blend, which is loaded with magnolia bark extract, grape seed extract, and vitamin E to help hydrate, reduce the appearance of redness, and improve skin resilience by promoting moisture retention. Light-Diffusing Mineral Powder reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles and helps even out skintone.'),
('P007', 'Creaseless Under Eye Concealer ', 'TARTE', 'Makeup', 'Face', 99.99, 'What it is:\r\nA vegan, full-coverage, creamy skincare concealer, now with 30 shades and a new applicator thatís totally foolproofóitís the same formula you love, but in new packaging.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nCreaseless Concealer completely covers dark circles, hyperpigmentation, redness, pimples, tattoos. The waterproof formula doesnít crease or sit in fine lines. Itís also powered by vitamin-C-rich maracuja for brighter, firmer-looking, and smoother-looking skin.'),
('P008', 'Killawatt Freestyle Highlighter', 'FENTY BEAUTY BY RIHA', 'Makeup', 'Face', 129.99, 'What it is:\r\nA line of weightless, long-wear cream-to-powder hybrid highlighters in solos and expertly paired duos. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nLight up where you want, when you want. Killawatt Freestyle Highlighter was born to reflect your every mood with its lineup of luminizing solos and duos. With a dose of skin-glorifying color, Killawatt ranges from subtle dayglow to insanely supercharged shades that were designed for all skin tones. \r\n\r\nUnlike your everyday highlighter, Killawatt keeps skin lit beyond sundown with its weightless long-wear formulaóa cream-powder hybrid that instantly melts into skin and blends with almost zero effort. Another win: Itís loaded with superfine shimmer for an ultra-smooth, creamy texture. \r\n\r\nFor killer radiance, Killawattís your go-to for highlighting your face, eyes, lips, collarboneÖ.literally anywhere you crave a touch of light.'),
('P009', 'Shimmering Skin Perfector Pressed Highlighter', 'BECCA', 'Makeup', 'Face', 179.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn award-winning highlighting powder with an ultra-buttery texture that melts into skin for the ultimate high-impact glow. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThis enhanced lineup of BECCAís iconic highlighter features an unparalleled shade range that caters to all skin tones. \r\n\r\nThis one-of-a-kind formula is enriched with ultra-fine, multitoned, luminescent pearls that adjust to your skinís undertones and amplify your natural radiance. Unlike traditional pressed powders, this unique formula blends pigments with liquids, creating a creamy feel that applies seamlessly and never cakes. Inspired by the dazzling light of the midday sun, the result is a high-impact, elegant finish that doesnít look glittery. \r\n'),
('P010', 'Translucent Loose Setting Powder ', 'LAURA MERCIER', 'Makeup', 'Face', 139.99, 'What it is: \r\nA cult-favorite and award-winning, silky powder with a touch of sheer coverage to set makeup for lasting wear. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nTranslucent Loose Setting Powder locks in makeup for long-lasting wear, without adding weight or texture. This bestseller creates a modern, matte finish with a touch of sheer coverage, while it absorbs oil and reduces shine all day. The pros know why it\'s their favorite: the powder is a little denser than an average powder, providing super smooth, even application and blending. This no-flashback formula means you\'ll look great in photos, and it creates a soft-focus effect to subtly blur the look of fine lines and imperfections. It will not settle into fine lines or pores and never looks cakey. These truly translucent shades work on all skin tonesófrom the fairest to the deepest. The just-released, Translucent Medium Deep shade was designed to be completely translucent on medium-deep to the deepest skin tones, ensuring that every skin tone gets a perfectly flawless, translucent finish. \r\n\r\nTranslucent: perfect for fair to medium and tan skin tones. \r\nTranslucent Medium Deep: Ideal for medium-deep to the deepest skin tones.\r\n'),
('P011', 'Eyeshadow Palette 28', 'NATASHA DENONA', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 799.99, 'What it is: \r\nAn eyeshadow palette with 28 shades that beautifully layer together for breathtaking eye looks. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nNatasha Denonaís Eyeshadow Palette 28 is ultra-pigmented, blends like a dream, and is long lasting. Enriched with moisturizing ingredients, itís made with real crushed pearls that create a radiant glow. The palette features an array of ultra-pigmented, unique shades and finishes. The revolutionary formula is smooth to the touch so that eye color glides seamlessly onto your lids while providing vivid color payoff with a silky-soft feel.'),
('P012', 'Soft Glam Eyeshadow Palette', 'ANASTASIA BEVERLY HILLS ', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 259.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn everyday to night palette with 14 shades, including essential mattes and glam shimmer finishes.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThis palette features 14 shades in ultra-matte, duo chrome, and metallic finishes that let you create softly-glamorous looks any time. Each shade is fully-pigmented and easy to blend. The palette is luxuriously packaged, with a large mirror and double-ended brush.\r\n'),
('P013', 'Better Than Sex Mascara', 'TOO FACED', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 64.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn intensely black, volumizing mascara with an hourglass-shaped brush that separates, coats, and curls each lash to voluptuous perfection.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nInspired by the curves of a womanís body, the hourglass-shaped brush was designed with extra stiff bristles to maximize the performance of this carbon black, collagen-fueled formula. One coat and lashes are full and defined. Two coats and lashes are even more luscious, curled, and dramatic. Three coats help you achieve the most intense, black, multidimensional lashes possible.'),
('P014', 'Diorshow Mascara', 'DIOR', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 126.99, 'What it is:\r\nA bestselling mascara, now with a conditioning formula thatís enriched with microfibers for a lash extension effect.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThe reinvented Diorshow Mascara features Diorís revolutionary patented AIR-LOCKô wiping system that keeps mascara fresh until the last useóas though you were using it on day one. Its original XXL Brush, a backstage makeup pro-inspired tool, is perfect for applying the versatile, microfiber-enhanced formula that gives buildable volume with each stroke. The formula\'s lash-care action helps smooth lashes for even more spectacular shape, coverage, and volume. With Dior\'s delicate signature rose essence, Diorshow Mascara elevates your lashes and your senses. Get fuller lashes, bolder impact, and a formula that lasts with this conditioning mascara.'),
('P015', 'Tattoo Liner', 'KAT VON D', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 79.99, 'What it is:\r\nA liquid eyeliner with an innovative brush tip for effortless, precise application. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nAchieve eye perfection with this high-pigment, waterproof liner that stays put all day for a fade-, melt-, crack-, and run-resistant finish. The superfine and flexible brush tip glides across the lashline for incredibly fluid application, allowing you to create a variety of looks with ease. Unlike traditional felt tip liners, this brush tip will not fray.'),
('P016', 'Stay All Day Waterproof Liquid Eye Liner', 'STILA', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 79.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn easy-application, waterproof liquid liner that stays on all day and night.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThis easy-glide, quick-dry precision liner stays in place until you say whenóno smudges, feathering, or running. The thin, marker-like tip is easy to use, even for the beauty beginner, and delivers any lookófrom a thin line to a bold, dramatic stroke. It goes on smoothly without skipping, smudging, or pulling, and lasts all day.'),
('P017', 'CILS BOOSTER XL Super-Enhancing Mascara Base', 'LANC‘ME', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 99.99, 'What it is:\r\nA lash-conditioning, mascara primer in the same great formula and new packaging that conditions and primes lashes to maximize resultsócreating even longer and more volumized lashes. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nGive your lashes an XL boost. With just one sweep, this innovative mascara primer glides on and evenly coats and smooths your lashes to maximize the results of your favorite mascara. The magic behind this mascara base is the conditioning formulaóinfused with micro-fibers and Vitamin Eó which adds extra length and thickness to lashes for added visible performance. White in color, it allows the black pigments to stand out from the clean base with more intensity than with traditional mascaras.'),
('P018', 'Eye Basics', 'LAURA MERCIER', 'Makeup', 'Eyes', 114.99, 'What it is:\r\nA water-resistant eyelid primer that camouflages imperfections and discolorations, while it enhances the durability of eye makeup. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nEye Basics provides the perfect canvas for eyelids to help eye color stay on longer. The highly versatile formula is water-resistant and crease-proof. Its sheer, creamy texture blends easily and smoothly, leaving a long-lasting, semi-matte finish.\r\n'),
('P019', 'Confession Lipstick Archive', 'HOURGLASS', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 2499.99, 'What it is:\r\nA limited-edition collectorís set of 30 Confession Ultra Slim Lipstick Refills paired with two sleek gold applicators to be used interchangeably with all Confession Refills. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nUltra Slim Lipstick delivers creamy, saturated, long-wearing color with a satin finish without smudging or feathering. Each ultra slim lipstick is designed to be used with the sleek gold applicators to provide the ultimate control to precisely accentuate, contour, and define the lips. The two gold applicators can be used interchangeably with the full collection of Confession Ultra Slim Lipstick Refills.'),
('P020', 'Amuse Bouche Lipstick', 'BITE BEAUTY', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 99.99, 'What it is: \r\nA collection of high-impact lipsticks in dimensional shades that have been handcrafted to deliver extreme moisture, soft texture, and creamy wear. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nSwipe on bold, creamy lip color with Bite Beautyís Amuse Bouche. Created and crafted by hand, Biteís small batch, low-heat process preserves a balanced blend of lip-quenching nutrients, vitamins, and omega oils that are essential for achieving healthy-looking lips. Made with 12 edible oils and triple milled pigments, this lipstick provides saturated lip color with weightless coverage and a citrus flavor made from fresh pressed fruit. '),
('P021', 'Lip Lacquer', 'TOM FORD', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 199.99, 'What it is:\r\nA lip lacquer that delivers pure, long-wearing color in three decadent formulas.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nTom Ford Lip Lacquer delivers pure, unadulterated liquid lip color in three decadent formulasóLiquid Matte, Liquid Metal, and Liquid Patent. Drenched in long-wearing, stay-true color, lips delight in the lightweight, comfortable textures infused with smoothing moisturizers.\r\n\r\nLiquid Patent formulas combine a lip stain with an ultra-glossy finish. Intense, vibrant shades evoke the transfixing look of skin-tight vinyl.\r\n\r\nLiquid Metal is an innovative liquid-gel with optical plumping effects. Pure metallic color with mirror-like dimension glides on with lustrous impact.\r\n\r\nLiquid Matte is rich and creamy upon application. The luxe formula transforms into feather-light, concentrated color in a fade-resistant, full-coverage, velvet matte finish.'),
('P022', 'Prime + Color Lip Gloss', 'TRÈSTIQUE', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 99.99, 'What it is:\r\nA two-in-one lip duo with primer and color for perfectly smooth, vibrant lip color that wears all day. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nSide one is an ultra-moisturizing lip primer that smooths and preps lips, creating the perfect canvas for color. The primer is infused with light-perfecting powders for a smoothing, soft focus effect. \r\n\r\nSide two is a color glaze. It glides on with a balmy feel and leaves lips with a soft shine and lasting stain. Lip Glaze is infused with coconut oil, which is known for its hydrating properties.'),
('P023', 'Gloss Bomb Universal Lip Luminizer ', 'FENTY BEAUTY BY RIHANNA', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 83.99, 'What it is: \r\nAn ultimate, gotta-have-it lip gloss with explosive shine that feels as good as it looksóin one universal rose nude shade. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nThis stop-everything, give-it-to-me gloss delivers explosive shine in one perfect rose nude shade handpicked by Rihanna herself: Fenty Glow. Weíre talking the unicorn of nudes that looks good on everyone. \r\n\r\nOne luscious swipe of Gloss Bombís XXL wand gives lips more to love, while conditioning shea butter enriches from within. Lips look instantly fuller and smoother. It feels amazing on your lipsówith a non-sticky formula thatís super shinyóand has an addictive peach-vanilla scent you just canít get enough of.\r\n'),
('P024', 'Enamored Hi-Shine Lip Lacquer Lipgloss', 'MARC JACOBS BEAUTY', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 104.99, 'What it is: \r\nA high-shine lip gloss in covetable shades with lasting brilliance. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nEnamored Hi-Shine Lip Lacquer lip gloss delivers maximum color and brilliance with its unique Triple Shine Complex, a blend of high-performance ingredients that provide unstoppable wear and shine like \"30 coats of lacquer.\" The brilliant shine contributes to an optical plumping look. And, Enamored feels cushiony on the lips, never sticky. This mint-scented lip gloss collection features a profusion of creamy pinks, shimmering lavenders, and iridescent brights that give lips a lush look with lasting color and unbelievable shine.'),
('P025', 'Velvet Matte Lipstick Pencil ', 'NARS', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 132.99, 'What it is:	\r\nA cult-favorite, matte lip pencil that instantly delivers the impact of a matte lipstick with the spontaneity of a pencil. \r\n\r\nWhat it does: \r\nThe NARS Velvet Pencil ensures that lips are instantly saturated with rich, vivid pigments and a velvety matte finish. Its jumbo size provides the application of a lipstick with the convenience of an artist pencil, and the tapered end is perfect for lining, defining, and filling in lips. Its non-drying formula is enriched with vitamin E and emollients for a creamy texture, while a blend of unique silicones ensures long-lasting, seamless matte color for hours. Just pair it with another lip product for added dimension or as a tinted base. Whether itís soft and neutral or bold and edgy, this lip pencil is ideal for making a lip statement. '),
('P026', 'Poutliner Longwear Lip Liner Pencil', 'MARC JACOBS BEAUTY', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 102.99, 'What it is:\r\nA collagen-infused, long-wear gel lip liner pencil. \r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThese gel-based, barely-there colors luxuriously line, define, and shape your lips, creating the perfect lasting canvas for lip color. Designed to work seamlessly with the full spectrum of Le Marc and New Nudes shades, these lip liners complement every lip coloróno matter how light, bright, or bold. Formulated with collagen to help fill in lines and prevent bleeding, this cream gel formula glides on flawlessly for all-day wear. '),
('P027', 'Full-On Lip Polish', 'BUXOM ', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 79.99, 'What it is:\r\nA bestselling gloss from the lip-plumping authority in a tingly, shimmer-sheer finishónow available in holographic, prismatic top coat shades.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nThis high-shine gloss tingles to coax a gorgeous lip look while pampering and moisturizing lips with vitamins A and E. Lips stay lusciously soft and seriously sexy. Layer on the love and take your look to the next level with new holographic top coats, which feature a unique silicone applicator. Full-On Lip Polish is also now available in prismatic special-effect pearl finishes.'),
('P028', 'Dior Addict Lacquer Plump', 'DIOR', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 129.99, 'What it is:\r\nA lip-plumping lacquered ink that provides intense, long-wear color and an incredibly comfortable texture.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nDior has pushed the boundaries of lip lacquer with the creation of their first lip-plumping lacquered ink. Like an ink, the lacquer dries down for a deeper saturation of color. It also tints the lips for up to eight hours.* A plumping effect delivers a more voluminous lip look and shaping effect, along with unprecedented hydration. Lips experience up to 78 percent increased moisture levels** for up to 24 hours after application.\r\n\r\nIts secret? An oil-in-water emulsion infused with pigments and hibiscus extract for a volumizing effect, paired with hyaluronic acid for rich hydration.'),
('P029', 'Orgasm Afterglow Lip Balm', 'NARS', 'Makeup', 'Lips', 106.99, 'What it is:\r\nA hydrating lip balm with a subtle hint of Orgasm color and a radiant finish.\r\n\r\nWhat it does:\r\nAfterglow Lip Balm delivers a sheer wash of the universally-flattering Orgasm shade with a radiant finish. The formula features NARSís MonoÔ Hydrating Complex for smooth, supple comfort. Itís also infused with a blend of antioxidant ingredients to help protect lips.'),
('P030', 'Ultimate Revival Cream', 'SK-II', 'Skincare', 'Moisturizer', 189.99, 'What it is:\r\nA rich, luxurious facial cream that works to enhance skin’s vitality and structure. \r\n\r\nWhat it is formulated to do:\r\nThis luxurious, incredibly powerful facial cream utilizes a combination of 15 ingredients blended together in a cutting-edge formula to enhance skin’s vitality and structure. It strengthens skin’s moisture barrier to maintain the skin over time.'),
('P031', 'ABSOLUE PREMIUM Bx - Absolute Night Recovery Cream', 'LANCÔME', 'Skincare', 'Moisturizer', 799.99, 'What it is: \r\nA nighttime replenishment that combines three advanced discoveries in one rich and soothing cream. \r\n\r\nWhat it is formulated to do: \r\nAge and hormonal changes are known to weaken skin at the structural level, leaving it dry, less elastic, and dull. Even a full night\'s sleep does not provide optimal recovery. With Absolue Night Premium ßx, Lancôme revolutionizes nighttime replenishment by combining three advanced discoveries in one rich and soothing cream. Pro-Xylane™, an exceptional and precise patented molecule that restores essential moisture so skin retains the appearance of youthful substance, firmness, and radiance—as if signs of aging are visibly repaired. The intensely replenishing ßio-Network™ complex—a blend of wild yam, soy, sea algae, and barley—helps enhance performance for visible rejuvenation. N-Stimuline™ helps support the natural recovery process so skin wakes up looking well-rested and luminous.'),
('P032', 'Lala Retro Whipped Cream', 'DRUNK ELEPHANT', 'Skincare', 'Moisturizer', 239.99, 'Which skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nOily\r\nCombination\r\nDry\r\nSensitive \r\n\r\nWhat it is:\r\nA retro-style moisturizer that rescues dry, dull skin while slowly delivering a steady dose of barrier moisture throughout the day and night.'),
('P033', 'Benefiance WrinkleResist24 Night Cream', 'SHISEIDO', 'Skincare', 'Moisturizer', 249.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn ultra-rich formula that helps improve visible signs of premature aging. \r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nDry \r\n'),
('P034', '100 percent Pure Argan Oil', 'JOSIE MARAN ', 'Skincare', 'Moisturizer', 99.99, 'What it is:\r\nA clinically proven 100 percent organic, do-it-all essential that naturally moisturizes and smooths fine lines and wrinkles to preserves skin\'s youthful radiance. \r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\n\r\nOily\r\nDry\r\nSensitive\r\n'),
('P035', 'Facial Treatment Essence ', 'SK-II', 'Skincare', 'Cleanser', 109.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn iconic essence with over 90 percent pitera.	\r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nOily\r\nCombination\r\nDry\r\nSensitive\r\n'),
('P036', 'Take The Day Off Cleansing Balm', 'CLINIQUE', 'Skincare', 'Cleanser', 119.99, 'What it is:\r\nA transformational, lightweight makeup remover that goes from balm to oil to milk to melt away every trace of eye and face makeup and sunscreen. \r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nOily\r\nCombination\r\nDry\r\nSensitive'),
('P037', 'Bi-Facil Double-Action Eye Makeup Remover', 'LANCÔME ', 'Skincare', 'Cleanser', 109.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn award-winning, gentle, liquid eye makeup remover. \r\n\r\nWhat it is formulated to do:\r\nThis formula activates when shaken to gently whisk away even waterproof eye makeup while conditioning and refreshing the skin. Ideal for sensitive skin and contact lenses, it leaves eyes feeling cool and relaxed without an oily residue.\r\n'),
('P038', 'Bye Bye Makeup 3-in-1 Makeup Melting Cleansing Ba', 'IT COSMETICS', 'Skincare', 'Cleanser', 155.99, 'What it is:\r\nA revolutionary, three-in-one cleanser, purifying makeup remover, and antiaging serum for better looking skin.\r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nOily\r\nCombination\r\nDry\r\nSensitive\r\n'),
('P039', 'Facial Treatment Clear Lotion Toner\r\n', 'SK-II', 'Skincare', 'Cleanser', 289.99, 'What it is:\r\nA hydrating toner to complete your cleansing ritual. \r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nOily\r\nCombination\r\nDry\r\nSensitive'),
('P040', 'Calendula Herbal Extract Alcohol Free Toner', 'KIEHL\'S SINCE 1851', 'Skincare', 'Cleanser', 199.99, 'What it is:\r\nAn effective, alcohol-free facial toner.\r\n\r\nWhich skin type is it good for?\r\nNormal\r\nOily '),
